title: ISO2USB GUI FullyPortable.7z
description:
Hi PS2 USB gamers ...

Ul.cfg is a very important file that needs stability to run the converted usb games correctly ...

This is a smart gui tool with instructions to convert perfectly the PS2 isos to the USB format to play in your FAT32 PS2 USB or Hard Drive ...

Works great for OpenPS2Loader but also have great compatability for USBAdvance , OpenUSBLoader or other USB games loaders ...



enjoy ...
